---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Sun's Lab & Life">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">About Me</p>
    <h1>About Sun</h1>
    <p>
      一个正在进入医学科研训练的临床医学学生。这里记录我如何在临床、科研、生信、
      摄影和生活里慢慢建立自己的节奏。
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-grid">
    <div class="info-card">
      <h2>Who I Am</h2>
      <p>
        Clinical medicine student, future professional master student, and a long-term learner
        interested in infectious diseases, tumor immunity, and bioinformatics.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-card">
      <h2>Why This Website</h2>
      <p>
        这个网站是我的数字小窝，也是我的长期成长档案。它会记录科研、学习、摄影和生活。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-card">
      <h2>Current Direction</h2>
      <p>
        ADCY7, tumor immunity, macrophage polarization, R workflows, and a sustainable life rhythm.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>